## Material Selection

### ðŸ“Œ Selected Material: **Aluminum 7475-T7651**

Chosen based on sensitivity, fatigue resistance, manufacturability, and fracture toughness.

- \( E = 10 \times 10^6 \, \text{psi} \)  
- \( \nu = 0.29 \)  
- \( \sigma_u \approx 65 \, \text{ksi} \)  
- \( K_{IC} \approx 46 \, \text{ksi}\sqrt{\text{in}} \)

This alloy allows a narrower reduced section while maintaining fatigue and crack-growth safety factors.

