## FEM Analysis

The modified wrench geometry was imported into **ANSYS Mechanical** for detailed evaluation.

Boundary conditions:

- Upper **0.40 in** of the square drive was fixed  
- A torsional load equivalent to **600 inÂ·lbf** was applied  

