This project demonstrates the complete design workflow for a sensor-integrated mechanical tool:

- Analytical modeling  
- CAD-based design refinement  
- FEM structural and strain analysis  
- Strain-gauge selection & Wheatstone-bridge integration  

The final design satisfies all structural performance requirements **and exceeds the required sensitivity**, producing **more than a 2Ã— improvement** over the baseline geometry.

